text: Saskia Bullen (born 20 July 1983) is a New Zealand cricketer. She played in three Women's Twenty20 International cricket (WT20I) matches between 2009 and 2010. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand women cricketers Category:New Zealand women Twenty20 International cricketers Category:Cricketers from Auckland
